                <p>
                    When the Amydus team was shown a demo of the SearchTap.io product, they were blown away by the speed
                    and accuracy of the search as you type technology. Loading times for search users were under 30
                    milliseconds and users had the option to use smart dynamic filters which automatically updated at
                    each keystroke.

                </p>

                <p>These features made sure that users were able to refine their query without leaving the search page.
                    For example, typing “dr” in the search field would show relevant results and filters for “dresses”.
                    These filters appeared to visitors across devices.
                </p>

                <img src="/img/success-stories/amydus/amydus-search-filters.jpg"
                     class="img-responsive center-block shadow-case mb40 max-width">


                <p>During the implementation process, SearchTap.io worked closely with the Amydus development team to
                    customize the search page to keep their visual design intact. UX/UI design for the mobile and
                    desktop platforms was refined. One of the first changes that SearchTap.io suggested was to make the
                    search bar prominent to make navigation simpler.
                </p>

                <img src="/img/success-stories/amydus/amydus-header.jpg"
                     class="img-responsive center-block shadow-case mb40 max-width">
                <img src="/img/success-stories/amydus/amydus-mobile-header.jpg"
                     class="img-responsive center-block shadow-case mb40 max-width"
                     style="width: 300px;">

                <p>With SearchTap.io, Amydus added distinct and easy to use native app type filters &amp; bubble filters
                    that enhanced the shopping experience tremendously. SearchTap.io also carefully optimized images to
                    make sure that results loaded promptly without comprising on their quality.
                </p>

                <p>The Amydus team now has access to the search data that was collected from the new search bar from
                    SearchTap.io. At Amydus, this search analytics is now a key input for product promotions, marketing
                    campaigns and even planning new product launches. The team is also using these insights to get a
                    better understanding of their website visitors and are actively using synonyms and data tags to
                    lower zero result searches and improve conversion rates.
                </p>


